data.description: Presenting a charming property boasting a spacious corner lot with a fenced backyard. Enjoy outdoor living with a covered deck and ample parking space. The property features a newer heat pump and a transferable warranty on the roof. Situated in a convenient neighborhood close to schools and shopping centers. Upstairs, the hardwood floors are protected by laminate and carpeting. One of the bedrooms has been converted into a functional office space. The primary bathroom offers a walk-in shower. Additionally, the kitchen's covered deck includes a gas stub and hot and cold water faucet. Downstairs, you'll find a large shop area, a bedroom, and a 3/4 bath. Lastly, the property showcases beautiful clear cedar siding, a rare find in today's market
